Molly kilete, Abuja The Nigerian Armyâ€™s Chief Of Army Staff (COAS) combined second and third quarter conference is currently ongoing in Abuja. The conference, which is aimed at reviewing army operations, is being attended by Principal Staff Officers from both the Defence and Army headquarters, General Officers Commanding, Commandants of Army schools and training institutions, Commanding Officers and heads of various Army operations in the country ,among other ranking personnel. The conference is taking place at the Command Army Officers Mess in Abuja. The conference, expected to end Thursday, would deliberate on the forthcoming elections in Bayelsa and Kogi states, national security challenges, resolving the challenges of prolonged troop deployments, among other matters.